# VitTrade UI Guardrails

Apply when editing under `flutter_app/`. Full rules: [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md).

## Shared primitives

Use `VitAppShell`, `VitPageLayout`, `VitPageContent`, `VitHeader`, `VitBottomNav`, `VitCard`, `VitCtaButton`, `VitInput`, `VitTabBar`, `VitSegmentedChoice`, `VitPresetChipRow` before local scaffolds.

Page rhythm (tiers, direct children, no orphan gaps): [vittrade-page-rhythm.mdc](./vittrade-page-rhythm.mdc).

Card tiles (Tier A fixed-height strips): [vittrade-card-tile.mdc](./vittrade-card-tile.mdc).

Service tile corner badges (Tier B safe inset): [vittrade-service-tile-badge.mdc](./vittrade-service-tile-badge.mdc).

Task cards (Tier E intrinsic height): [vittrade-task-card.mdc](./vittrade-task-card.mdc).

Accent icon boxes (module row icons): [vittrade-accent-icon-box.mdc](./vittrade-accent-icon-box.mdc).

Segment pills (tabs/toggles/filter chips): [vittrade-segment-pill.mdc](./vittrade-segment-pill.mdc).

## Theme tokens

Use `AppColors`, `AppSpacing`, `AppRadii`, `AppTextStyles` from `flutter_app/lib/app/theme/`. No new `BorderRadius.circular()` outside `app_radii.dart`.

## Product boundaries

- **Open Arena:** points-only — no wallet, payout, profit, or stake-return language.
- **Prediction Markets:** positions, probability, receipts, rewards, P/L allowed.
- **Financial flows:** preview/confirm for withdrawals, escrow, security, P2P payment changes.

## UI polish

For review/polish passes, read `.codex/skills/vittrade-ui-checklists/SKILL.md`.

Minimal diff policy (how to write, not what to use): [vittrade-minimal-diff.mdc](../../.cursor/rules/vittrade-minimal-diff.mdc).
